data/stories/
  Original simplified Japanese folk tale texts and English adaptations.
  The underlying folk tales (Momotarō, Urashima Tarō, Kaguya-hime, Tsuru no Ongaeshi,
  Issun Bōshi) are ancient works in the public domain in all jurisdictions.
  English text adapted from Yei Theodora Ozaki's translations (1908), also public domain.
  These story files are released under Creative Commons Zero (CC0 1.0).
  https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

fonts/KleeOne-SemiBold.ttf, fonts/OFL-KleeOne.txt
